{"tid":981541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我憧憬既畫師 - 大暮維人","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T13:04:54.000Z","uid":216800,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"86c93217026e9ef399c1c8f1a84ec8dd224ab4a8","tid":981541,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"由細細個鍾意畫公仔到第一次接觸飛輪少年<br />\n大暮維人向我展現既唔單止喺公仔咁簡單<br />\n喺一個<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藝術</span></span><br />\n由果時開始 我目標定咗係大暮維人嘅畫功上<br />\n<br />\n有一日心血來潮 決定模仿佢一頁漫畫<br />\nいくぞ！！我嘅憧憬畫師！大暮維人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">首先畫柒張草稿出黎</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ntkiQJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ntkiQJ.png&h=b6128b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">然後由主體開始 勾條靚線</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwDXk4X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwDXk4X.png&h=af16bb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第一格大致勾完</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zR6J05A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzR6J05A.png&h=5f3c407b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落網搞柒佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得！<br />\n得咗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9hUokb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9hUokb.png&h=9773134c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第二格</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNbmNNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNbmNNU.png&h=31a6b820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勾柒佢！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXK0iUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXK0iUZ.png&h=a8aca269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">補黑位</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6weom8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6weom8.png&h=9f028718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再落網搞柒佢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXBFiVR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXBFiVR.png&h=37c741d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baeea845ff34feb272a00e05145bfdae30668f5","tid":981541,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"天上天下？"},{"pid":"f0baf5cbc5de835aa377065f04d65e9e0553441e","tid":981541,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"第一張都ban得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cd693fa4b42af4ec37d79bb0a887914db4c114","tid":981541,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3baeea845ff34feb272a00e05145bfdae30668f5","tid":981541,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"天上天下？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14